  "description": "<em>Story Machine</em> is a product aimed at children for teaching language skills. <br><br>The product contains animations assigned to key nouns, and verbs. By typing phrases such as &quot;The Girl Jumps Over the Flower&quot; will show the player an animation of a girl jumping over a flower. Through this method, players are able to create short &quot;stories&quot; of about 40 words long and have the computer animate them. These stories are also limited to having 4 &quot;actors&quot; (animated noun objects) in each.",
